 Address.use    code            home | work | temp | old | billing - purpose of this address
 Address.type   code            postal | physical | both
 Address.text   string          Text representation of the address
 Address.line       string          Street name, number, direction & P.O. Box etc.
 Address.city       string          Name of city, town etc.
 Address.district       string          District name (aka county)
 Address.state      string          Sub-unit of country (abbreviations ok)
 Address.postalCode     string          Postal code for area
 Address.country        string          Country (e.g. may be ISO 3166 2 or 3 letter code)
 Address.period     Period          Time period when address was/is in use